<view class="container">
  <!-- 步骤1: 选文件 -->
  <view wx:if="{{step === 1}}">
    <view class="card">
      <view class="form-item">
        <text class="form-label">📥 选择成绩Excel</text>
        <view class="upload-area" bindtap="chooseFile">
          <view wx:if="{{uploading}}" class="uploading">
            <text>解析中...</text>
          </view>
          <view wx:elif="{{fileName}}" class="file-info">
            <text class="file-name">📊 {{fileName}}</text>
            <text class="file-change">点击重新选择</text>
          </view>
          <view wx:else class="upload-placeholder">
            <text class="upload-icon">+</text>
            <text>从聊天记录中选择Excel</text>
          </view>
        </view>
      </view>
    </view>

    <view class="card">
      <view class="card-title">📋 格式要求</view>
      <view class="format-desc">
        Excel 第一行需包含:
      </view>
      <view class="format-list">
        <view class="color-tag tag-blue">姓名(必填)</view>
        <view class="color-tag tag-green">科目列(如:物理/语文/数学,自动全导入)</view>
        <view class="color-tag tag-purple">班级(可选,有则自动分班)</view>
        <view class="color-tag tag-cyan">年级(可选,8→初二, 9→初三)</view>
      </view>
      <view class="format-desc" style="margin-top: 16rpx;">
        示例: 姓名 | 年级 | 班级 | 物理 | 语文 | 数学
      </view>
      <view class="tip-text" style="margin-top: 12rpx;">
        💡 所有科目列一次性全部导入,系统自动按年级填充满分默认值(可手动修改)。有"年级"+"班级"列时自动组合班级名(8年级+01→初二1班),匹配已有班级或自动创建。
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <!-- 步骤2: 预览确认 -->
  <view wx:if="{{step === 2 && previewData}}">
    <view class="card">
      <view class="card-title">⚙️ 导入设置</view>

      <view class="form-item">
        <text class="form-label">📝 考试名称</text>
        <input class="form-input" placeholder="如:期中考试" value="{{examName}}" bindinput="onExamInput" />
      </view>

      <view class="form-item" wx:if="{{hasClassColumn && !hasGradeColumn}}">
        <text class="form-label">🎓 年级前缀</text>
        <input class="form-input" placeholder="如:初二" value="{{gradePrefix}}" bindinput="onGradeInput" />
        <view class="tip-text" style="margin-top: 8rpx;">
          检测到"班级"列但无"年级"列,输入年级前缀后自动匹配/创建班级
        </view>
      </view>

      <view class="form-item" wx:if="{{hasGradeColumn}}">
        <text class="form-label">🎓 年级</text>
        <view class="form-picker">✅ 已从Excel自动识别</view>
      </view>

      <view class="form-item">
        <text class="form-label">💯 各科满分(可修改)</text>
        <view class="full-score-list">
          <view wx:for="{{subjects}}" wx:key="*this" class="full-score-item">
            <text class="full-score-subject">{{item}}</text>
            <input class="full-score-input" type="digit" value="{{fullScores[item]}}" data-subject="{{item}}" bindinput="onFullScoreInput" />
            <text class="full-score-unit">分</text>
          </view>
        </view>
      </view>
    </view>

    <view class="card">
      <view class="card-title">👁️ 预览 ({{previewData.total_students}}人 · {{subjects.length}}科)</view>
      <scroll-view scroll-x>
        <view class="preview-table">
          <view class="preview-row preview-header-row">
            <text class="preview-cell">姓名</text>
            <text class="preview-cell" wx:if="{{hasGradeColumn}}">年级</text>
            <text class="preview-cell" wx:if="{{hasClassColumn}}">班级</text>
            <text class="preview-cell" wx:for="{{subjects}}" wx:key="*this">{{item}}</text>
          </view>
          <view wx:for="{{previewData.students}}" wx:key="index" class="preview-row">
            <text class="preview-cell">{{item.name}}</text>
            <text class="preview-cell" wx:if="{{hasGradeColumn}}">{{item.grade || '-'}}</text>
            <text class="preview-cell" wx:if="{{hasClassColumn}}">{{item.class_name || '-'}}</text>
            <text class="preview-cell" wx:for="{{subjects}}" wx:for-item="subj" wx:key="*this">{{item.scores[subj] !== null && item.scores[subj] !== undefined ? item.scores[subj] : '-'}}</text>
          </view>
        </view>
      </scroll-view>
    </view>

    <view class="btn-primary save-btn {{importing ? 'disabled' : ''}}" bindtap="confirmImport">
      {{importing ? '导入中...' : '📥 确认导入全部科目'}}
    </view>
    <view class="btn-cancel-text" bindtap="reset">重新选择文件</view>
  </view>
</view>
